    "Text": "\n    <p>Free software emulation of curses in System V.</p>\n  "
  },
  "Description": {
    "Text": "\n    <p>Multiple vulnerabilities have been discovered in ncurses. Please review\n      the CVE identifiers referenced below for details.\n    </p>\n  "
  },
